{
  "stem": "14091.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 481.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When I was thrown in there, I felt I was alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I also felt some other people were moving.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [CRYING] But I lay there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "When everything stopped, it was very dark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And everybody left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They didn't close the pit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "Because, apparently, the thought that they would still collect people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] I decided I will try to crawl out of there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And I first crawled-- I was in the middle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I first had to crawl to the- to one of the sides.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And from there, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "Apparently, my will was so strong that I managed to crawl out of there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "But I was so soaked in blood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And my shoes came off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "I was barefoot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "My hair were all soaked in blood, my clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And I got out of there, and I start running.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "I didn't know where, but from far away, I saw light.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And, apparently, it must've been a small farm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I ran to this house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "I knocked at the door, and a woman came out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "She saw me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "And, apparently, she must have thought I'm a devil or something, because-- you could imagine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "And it was so cold that my hair became like icicles, like red icicles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "And she saw me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And I asked her if she could give me something to put on my feet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "And she gave me-- not shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "She gave me, like not bandages-- like, like [NON-ENGLISH], like old rags and some rope.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "And I bound-- I-- I put it on my feet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "And I told the rope and closed it up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "And she gave me some bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
